<item>
            <title>[HTTPCLIENT-1946] Support relatively new HTTP 308 redirect - RFC7538</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HTTPCLIENT-1946</link>
                <project id="12310360" key="HTTPCLIENT">HttpComponents HttpClient</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;RFC7538 added a new HTTP redirect code: 308.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To support it all you need is adding 2 rows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In HttpStatus add constant: SC_PERMANENT_REDIRECT = 308&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In HttpMethodDirector.isRedirectNeeded() (in version 3.x) add SC_PERMANENT_REDIRECT to the switch clause.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
                <environment>Irrelevant</environment>
